  "panels": [
    {
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "id": 100,
      "options": {
        "content": "### How To Read\n- **AI Request Rate / Latency P95**: chat 和 summary 的端到端请求吞吐与耗时。\n- **First Token / Stream Duration P95**: 专门看流式体验，不和总耗时混在一起。\n- **Route Distribution / Retrieval Context P95**: 看 chat 到底在走哪条 route，以及用了多少证据上下文。\n- **Summary Cache Lookup / Token Usage / Answer Length**: 看 summary 是否命中缓存，模型是否更烧 token，以及回答长度是否漂移。\n- **Quality Proxy Rates**: 用 follow-up、复制、citation 打开这些用户行为估算回答可用性和稳定性。\n- **Online Review Scores / Bad Cases**: 对抽样回答做 groundedness、faithfulness、completeness 的在线 judge。",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "title": "How To Read",
      "transparent": true,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "description": "每秒 AI 请求数，按操作、模式和状态拆分。",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "decimals": 2,
          "unit": "reqps"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 4 },
      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom" },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "notebooklm:ai_requests_total:rate5m",
          "legendFormat": "{{operation}} / {{mode}} / {{status}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "AI Request Rate (5m)",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
